Feature: Using oven to heat room
  As a renter in a northeastern city
  I can use the oven to heat a room during the winter months
  So that I can keep heating costs down

Feature: Using oven to store pots/pans
    As a dweller in a small apt/condo/house
    I can use the oven to store pots/pans
    So that I can use the cabinet space for other kitchen materials

  Feature: Using oven to slow cook food
      As a very active and time conscious parent
      I can use the oven to slowly and safely cook meals
      So that I can use my time to do other activities
